SUMMARY:P.F.Chang's Paint Party! Blazing Sunset 
DESCRIPTION:Pop Up Paint and Sip\nP.F. Chang's in The Streets of [Tanasbourne!](https://www.pfchangs.com/locations/us/or/hillsboro/10088-ne-emma-way/9200-tanasbourne.html)\n\n10088 NW Emma Way\, Hillsboro\, OR 97124\n\n**ALL AGES WELCOME**\n**SEATING IS LIMITED!**\nPlease remember to arrive 10 minutes early.\n**THIS IS A NEW PAINTING OPTION!**\n[Carrie](https://www.carolinegreenart.com/) will be guiding you how to create a beautiful blazing sunset at the coast painting! All supplies for your painting are included.\n\n\\*This venue holds 20\n\nAll materials for your painting are included!\n**Tickets $40**\nNo experience necessary\, judgment free zone!\n**EXTRA TICKETS HERE: [https://www.paintandsipportland.com/](https://www.paintandsipportland.com/)**\n\\*Food and drink not included in ticket price.
