SUMMARY:Paint & Sip- Multnomah Falls at Steeplejack Hillsboro
DESCRIPTION:Pop Up Paint and Sip\nOrder dinner\, grab a beverage and join us for this fun\, step-by-step painting experience at [SteepleJack Brewing](https://www.steeplejackbeer.com/location/steeplejack-hillsboro) in **Hillsboro!**\nWe will be meeting in the back room\, located to your right as you walk in\, past the bar.\n\n**SEATING IS LIMITED! This venue holds 19 spots!**\n\n[Carrie](https://www.carolinegreenart.com/) will be guiding you how to create a beautiful Multnomah Falls painting. **This one is a new painting!**\nAll supplies for your painting are included.\n\n**Tickets $40**\nNo experience necessary\, judgment free zone!\nEXTRA TICKETS HERE: [https://www.paintandsipportland.com/](https://www.paintandsipportland.com/)\n(\\*Food and Drink NOT provided\, but you are welcome to buy)
