SUMMARY:Good Morning\, Sunshine! Paint and Sip- Steeplejack SW PDX
DESCRIPTION:Pop Up Paint and Sip\nJoin us for food and drinks at [Steeplejack](https://www.steeplejackbeer.com/location/steeplejack-pizza-and-beer) located on\n**Beaverton Hillsdale Highway.**\n**Not to be confused with the Hillsboro or Hawthorne locations.**\n\\* We will be meeting to the right as you walk in!\n\nThis venue holds 20 painters.\n\n**THIS IS A NEW PAINTING OPTION!**\n[Carrie](https://www.carolinegreenart.com/) will be showing you easy steps to create this beautiful morning sunrise over Mt Hood!!\n\nAll materials for your painting are included!\nNo experience necessary\, judgment free zone!\nTickets $40\nEXTRA TICKETS HERE: [https://www.paintandsipportland.com/](https://www.paintandsipportland.com/)\n(\\*Food and Drink NOT provided\, but you are welcome to buy)
